<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>NF Calc — Grupo 17</title>
  <style>
    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    :root {
      --bg:     #0f172a;
      --surface:#1e293b;
      --border: #334155;
      --accent: #10b981;
      --accent2:#059669;
      --text:   #f1f5f9;
      --muted:  #94a3b8;
    }
    body {
      background: var(--bg);
      color: var(--text);
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', system-ui, sans-serif;
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      padding: 2rem;
      position: relative;
    }
    .back {
      position: fixed;
      top: 1.25rem;
      left: 1.5rem;
      color: var(--muted);
      text-decoration: none;
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      transition: color 0.15s;
    }
    .back:hover { color: var(--text); }
    .badge {
      background: rgba(16,185,129,0.12);
      border: 1px solid rgba(16,185,129,0.25);
      color: var(--accent);
      font-size: 0.72rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: 0.1em;
      padding: 4px 14px;
      border-radius: 100px;
      margin-bottom: 1.75rem;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }
    h1 {
      font-size: clamp(2.75rem, 7vw, 4.5rem);
      font-weight: 800;
      line-height: 1.05;
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    }
    h1 span { color: var(--accent); }
    .tagline {
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 1.05rem;
      max-width: 460px;
      text-align: center;
      line-height: 1.65;
      margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    }
    .cta {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.5rem;
      background: var(--accent);
      color: #000;
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      padding: 0.9rem 2.25rem;
      border-radius: 8px;
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: background 0.2s, transform 0.15s;
      margin-bottom: 3.5rem;
    }
    .cta:hover { background: var(--accent2); transform: translateY(-2px); }
    .features {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 1rem;
      max-width: 600px;
      width: 100%;
    }
    @media (max-width: 520px) { .features { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }
    .feature {
      background: var(--surface);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 10px;
      padding: 1.25rem;
    }
    .feature-icon { font-size: 1.4rem; margin-bottom: 0.6rem; }
    .feature h3 { font-size: 0.82rem; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 0.3rem; }
    .feature p  { font-size: 0.76rem; color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.45; }
    footer {
      position: fixed;
      bottom: 1.25rem;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 0.72rem;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <a class="back" href="/">← Início</a>

  <div class="badge">Grupo 17 · GCEIC 2026</div>
  <h1>NF <span>Calc</span></h1>
  <p class="tagline">Calcule ICMS, IPI, PIS e COFINS de qualquer Nota Fiscal de Venda a partir da chave de acesso NF-e.</p>

  <% if (user) { %>
    <a class="cta" href="<%= basePath %>/calcular">Abrir calculadora →</a>
  <% } else { %>
    <a class="cta" href="<%= basePath %>/login">Entrar no sistema →</a>
  <% } %>

  <div class="features">
    <div class="feature">
      <div class="feature-icon">🔑</div>
      <h3>Chave NF-e</h3>
      <p>Decodifica estado, CNPJ, modelo, série e dígito verificador automaticamente.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="feature">
      <div class="feature-icon">📊</div>
      <h3>4 Impostos</h3>
      <p>ICMS por estado, IPI, PIS e COFINS com alíquotas corretas por regime.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="feature">
      <div class="feature-icon">🏢</div>
      <h3>3 Regimes</h3>
      <p>Lucro Real, Lucro Presumido e Simples Nacional com um clique.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <footer>NF Calc · Grupo 17 · GCEIC 2026</footer>
</body>
</html>
